ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v251.segment

Class RQ1

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractSegment
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v251.segment.RQ1
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Segment, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class RQ1
extends AbstractSegment

    Represents an HL7 RQ1 message segment (Requisition Detail-1). This segment has the following fields:

    • RQ1-1: Anticipated Price (ST) optional
    • RQ1-2: Manufacturer Identifier (CE) optional
    • RQ1-3: Manufacturer's Catalog (ST) optional
    • RQ1-4: Vendor ID (CE) optional
    • RQ1-5: Vendor Catalog (ST) optional
    • RQ1-6: Taxable (ID) optional
    • RQ1-7: Substitute Allowed (ID) optional
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
